From bff8236d281649f0eb438eb6fb522cb15b7e9faf Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Slick <slick@slicksync.local>
Date: Sun, 12 Jul 2026 05:20:16 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: new custom logo, distinct from original SlickSync branding

Replaced the plain circular 'S' badge inherited from upstream SlickSync
with an original angular spark mark, gradient violet-to-cyan matching
the existing Slick theme palette (globals.css --color-primary /
--color-secondary). Regenerated logo-white.png, logo-black.png,
favicon.ico, favicon-16x16.png, favicon-32x32.png, and
apple-touch-icon.png from a single SVG source. No component code
changes needed - all existing <img> references and the layout.tsx
icon metadata already point at these filenames.

Bump to 1.9.13, changelog entry added.
---
 client/public/apple-touch-icon.png | Bin 8144 -> 4328 bytes
 client/public/changelog.json       |  10 ++++++++++
 client/public/favicon-16x16.png    | Bin 389 -> 372 bytes
 client/public/favicon-32x32.png    | Bin 813 -> 699 bytes
 client/public/favicon.ico          | Bin 15406 -> 1032 bytes
 client/public/logo-black.png       | Bin 89028 -> 15702 bytes
 client/public/logo-white.png       | Bin 90169 -> 15702 bytes
 package.json                       |   2 +-
 8 files changed, 11 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

